{
  "stem": "4187.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he had a girlfriend, a beautiful young woman, [GERMAN], and of course, called Marguerite.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had a love affair, a big love affair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And needless to say, Jews were not allowed near that building, of course.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And who'd want to go there, anyway?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had, in my block, there was this unfortunate woman who was-- [POINTING] I think, she was already gone.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And something happened to her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure what it was, but something that she didn't like one night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she marched up to the commandant's house and banged the door and went in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was the commander with Marguerite in bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you can imagine the welcome.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the German, I think, literally kicked-- literally kicked her out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She flew out and-- and landed on the ground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was picked up by another German, probably SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And because of what she's done, she was beaten up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she went back to the commandant to complain that she was beaten up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he killed her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beat her to death.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was beaten to the extent where she died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that-- the other thing that I want to tell you about-- about Duderstadt was that a woman in my-- in the room that I was, was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, this is-- this was still well-- with the Hungarians, she got pregnant before she was taken.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because this is only still November.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was plenty-- only six months in camp at that stage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she was-- what I'm trying to say is she was not pregnant to a German, but pregnant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How she survived being pregnant, I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That-- that was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But Germans didn't notice, whatever, but she did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she gave birth in Duderstadt.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
